title: Top 10 American Horror Story Moments
author: WatchMojo.com
comment: Lana's escape was the most satisfying TV moment I've ever had the pleasure of watching.

Twisty The Clown's story broke my heart. "I'm so dumb, I can't even kill myself" that was literally the saddest shit I ever heard 😟😟😟

edit I had no idea this comment would get so many likes.
When Violet found her body I was shook
Finding out the daughter in season 1 was dead the whole time was the biggest plot twist in television. I actually gasped watching it.
I hate clowns. But Twisty has a special place in my heart, such a sad backstory
